1
00:01:36,820 --> 00:01:40,040
[Episode 14]

2
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,932
Only He Bo and his death soldiers

3
00:01:45,932 --> 00:01:47,760
can enter or exit this secret tunnel.

4
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,519
Where exactly this tunnel leads

5
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:52,360
and what dangers lie ahead are unknown.

6
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,571
You sure?

7
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,460
Thank you again, Moon Envoy,

8
00:01:58,460 --> 00:02:00,680
for helping me.

9
00:02:07,639 --> 00:02:08,680
Once I go inside,

10
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,039
you should leave immediately.

11
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:12,972
Lest you and Hanshui Palace get involved.

12
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,667
Brother Zhan,

13
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,670
please be very careful.

14
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:23,000
Greetings, He Bo.

15
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:38,541
Rise.

16
00:05:38,541 --> 00:05:41,719
[Soaring to the Heavens]

17
00:05:41,719 --> 00:05:44,879
Those people from the Yunying Sect...
have they not succeeded yet?

18
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:48,181
He Bo, they have already returned.

19
00:05:51,729 --> 00:05:54,330
[Soaring to the Heavens]

20
00:05:57,840 --> 00:06:00,440
Tang Sect and Shengyun Stronghold

21
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,720
have fought over the Chang Hong Bi.

22
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,919
I thought it was

23
00:06:03,919 --> 00:06:08,400
due to the long-standing feud between them.

24
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,599
It turns out

25
00:06:10,599 --> 00:06:14,640
the Tang Sect was acting on your orders.

26
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,919
He Bo,

27
00:06:15,919 --> 00:06:18,039
you ordered your subordinates

28
00:06:18,039 --> 00:06:21,039
to challenge every major sect.

29
00:06:21,039 --> 00:06:24,380
Any sect leader who refused to be driven by you

30
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:27,679
ended up killed by you.

31
00:06:27,679 --> 00:06:31,159
You have been so calculating

32
00:06:31,159 --> 00:06:32,919
all for the sake of

33
00:06:32,919 --> 00:06:35,400
dominating the martial world, right?

34
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:39,239
Since you know
the fate of those stubborn fools, Chief Jiao,

35
00:06:39,239 --> 00:06:40,559
you should understand that

36
00:06:40,559 --> 00:06:42,159
sparing your life

37
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:45,064
is already an act of great mercy.

38
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,980
You...

39
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:53,280
You dare to dream
of unifying the martial world,

40
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:55,440
but why

41
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:58,479
do you not dare to show your true face,

42
00:06:58,479 --> 00:07:00,662
Jing Yi Ming?

43
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,159
I heard you spent years

44
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,679
studying this sword technique.

45
00:07:34,679 --> 00:07:36,760
Yet, it only took me seven days

46
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,679
to find the weakness of it.

47
00:07:38,679 --> 00:07:41,440
It seems the famous Shengyun Stronghold

48
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,320
will fall into ruin under your leadership.

49
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:47,999
Enough talk. Kill me if you want to.

50
00:07:48,999 --> 00:07:51,479
You are a renowned figure.

51
00:07:51,479 --> 00:07:54,119
It would be a pity to kill you.

52
00:07:54,119 --> 00:07:56,239
With the birthday banquet approaching,

53
00:07:56,239 --> 00:07:57,760
I will give you two choices.

54
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:58,919
First,

55
00:07:58,919 --> 00:08:01,479
persuade those old fogies,

56
00:08:01,479 --> 00:08:04,679
and make them willing to serve under me.

57
00:08:04,679 --> 00:08:06,880
Second, you become like them.

58
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,520
Be a walking dead,

59
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,559
and eliminate those stubborn fools

60
00:08:10,559 --> 00:08:13,159
one by one.

61
00:08:13,159 --> 00:08:15,080
Which path do you choose?

62
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,799
It's entirely up to you,

63
00:08:16,799 --> 00:08:18,159
Chief Jiao.

64
00:08:18,159 --> 00:08:20,599
What if I choose neither?

65
00:08:20,599 --> 00:08:24,789
What can you do to me?

66
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:29,599
It seems Chief Jiao has made his choice.

67
00:08:29,599 --> 00:08:32,646
Once you ingest this Yemotian Poison,

68
00:08:32,646 --> 00:08:34,860
there is no turning back.

69
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:38,343
Once it enters your body,
it seeps into the heart and mind,

70
00:08:38,343 --> 00:08:40,159
and will cause constant hallucinations.

71
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:42,599
From now on, you will only obey
the sound of the bell.

72
00:08:42,599 --> 00:08:46,039
Even if I order you to kill yourself,
you will not hesitate.

73
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,880
What an ingenious drug.

74
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,239
Its antidote is the poison itself.

75
00:08:50,239 --> 00:08:52,440
Only by taking Yemotian Poison again

76
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,960
can the hallucinations be suppressed.

77
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:56,520
A short cure that rots the mind.

78
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:59,239
Each dose leaves you more witless than before.

79
00:08:59,239 --> 00:09:01,200
A few days ago, he disguised himself
as me and went to the island.

80
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,120
He tricked my brothers
into drinking the poison.

81
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,721
The poison isn't lethal,

82
00:09:04,721 --> 00:09:07,080
but it makes one lose their mind
and suffer hallucinations.

83
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,000
Where did you hide the Yicheng magistrate?

84
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,960
You are truly determined to work for Zhi Hua.

85
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,083
Where did you hide the Yicheng magistrate?

86
00:09:13,083 --> 00:09:14,880
Bai Yu Tang,

87
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,720
don't take a step you cannot undo.

88
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:19,665
Then I shall find him myself.

89
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:26,180
Be quiet.

90
00:09:37,239 --> 00:09:38,479
Jiao Chao Gui,

91
00:09:38,479 --> 00:09:40,640
you should think this through.

92
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:42,359
A great leader of Shengyun Stronghold.

93
00:09:42,359 --> 00:09:44,320
Is this how you want to end?

94
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:47,754
With no honor?

95
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,359
Zhan Zhao,

96
00:10:24,359 --> 00:10:26,320
I know why you're here.

97
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,960
You are here to save her.

98
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,279
I've long heard
the Southern Knight's skill is unmatched.

99
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,700
I'd like to test that for myself.

100
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:45,840
If you can defeat me today,

101
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:49,190
you may take her with you.

102
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,080
Zhan Zhao.

103
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,200
You learned it from the swordsman, Xia Yu Qi.

104
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,160
His swordsmanship is almost unrivaled,

105
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:42,210
but there are still a few flaws.

106
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,239
He Bo,

107
00:12:20,239 --> 00:12:22,720
the outcome of our duel has been decided.

108
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,880
Continue?

109
00:12:57,920 --> 00:13:00,040
Zhan Zhao,

110
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:04,190
what do you think of my Dragon Roar Swordplay?

111
00:13:07,599 --> 00:13:10,519
You may have stolen techniques
from countless masters.

112
00:13:10,519 --> 00:13:12,239
But you know the moves,

113
00:13:12,239 --> 00:13:14,530
not the meaning behind them.

114
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,720
Do you think you can dominate
the martial world this way?

115
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:20,330
How ridiculous.

116
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:37,776
Where did you learn these skills?

117
00:14:40,119 --> 00:14:42,783
From my Zhan family.

118
00:14:43,399 --> 00:14:44,960
Jing Yi Ming.

119
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:48,074
Still hiding the tricks
of your own sect?

120
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:27,279
The world is full of heroes.

121
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:29,080
Each with their own unique skills.

122
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,840
Even if you spend ten lifetimes,

123
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,960
you can't steal every sect's unique skills

124
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:35,853
for yourself.

125
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:50,786
Everyone, kill Zhan Zhao!

126
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:41,692
[Soaring to the Heavens]

127
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:52,024
The Zhanlu Sword.

128
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,940
Hurry up. Search every inch of this place!

129
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:39,020
Yes.

130
00:18:42,479 --> 00:18:44,755
Check over there.

131
00:18:54,279 --> 00:18:56,479
Brother Zhan, come with me.

132
00:18:56,479 --> 00:18:58,584
This way.

133
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,160
Miss Huo.

134
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,360
Any news of Brother Zhan?

135
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:40,839
Still inside the secret tunnel.

136
00:19:40,839 --> 00:19:43,759
I knew you'd be troubled,
so I came to tell you this.

137
00:19:43,759 --> 00:19:46,079
He's been in there for so long.

138
00:19:46,079 --> 00:19:47,360
Can't wait.

139
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:49,720
Don't go. Brother Zhan
wouldn't let you act rashly either.

140
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,880
But I'm afraid he's in danger.

141
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:54,239
Wait for the time it takes
an incense stick to burn.

142
00:19:54,239 --> 00:19:55,279
If he doesn't come out,

143
00:19:55,279 --> 00:19:57,820
I'll go with you to save him.

144
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:03,684
Brother Zhan.

145
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:07,839
How did you get here?

146
00:20:07,839 --> 00:20:09,279
Was that Moon Envoy?

147
00:20:09,279 --> 00:20:10,799
Yes.

148
00:20:10,799 --> 00:20:12,640
Where is she?

149
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:16,635
Let's go. We should head back first.

150
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,360
Zhao Hui, we have confirmed

151
00:20:44,360 --> 00:20:46,600
that Jing Yi Ming
has been using Zhongxiao Pavilion

152
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:48,519
to buy off officials for Lord of Xiangyang

153
00:20:48,519 --> 00:20:50,360
and win over martial world figures.

154
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,440
The crime he committed

155
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:53,720
was the high treason for subverting the realm.

156
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:55,039
I came here this time

157
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:57,600
specifically to bring him to justice.

158
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,720
My appearance at his house tonight

159
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:03,039
was also to search for evidence.

160
00:21:03,039 --> 00:21:04,600
I see.

161
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:05,857
I am staying at his house.

162
00:21:05,857 --> 00:21:07,759
Besides wanting to investigate
during the birthday banquet,

163
00:21:07,759 --> 00:21:09,160
I am also truly worried

164
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,519
that Yue Hua might choose this time

165
00:21:10,519 --> 00:21:12,883
to seek revenge on Jing Yi Ming.

166
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:15,039
By the way,

167
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:17,120
I've been at his house for days now.

168
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:18,441
I have found some clues.

169
00:21:18,441 --> 00:21:20,970
I don't know if it'll help your investigation.

170
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:23,279
Tell me.

171
00:21:23,279 --> 00:21:24,680
Ever since I moved into his place,

172
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:27,279
Jing Yi Ming has had a small courtyard
guarded day and night.

173
00:21:27,279 --> 00:21:29,239
Whenever I got close to that courtyard,

174
00:21:29,239 --> 00:21:32,754
I could always smell a faint medicinal scent.

175
00:21:39,999 --> 00:21:42,332
What's wrong? By the look of you,

176
00:21:42,332 --> 00:21:45,839
you already know who's locked in there.

177
00:21:45,839 --> 00:21:47,415
We do.

178
00:21:48,159 --> 00:21:49,800
But that matter

179
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:51,480
isn't related to your family's case.

180
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:54,398
So we won't go into the details.

181
00:21:55,079 --> 00:21:56,240
Zhao Hui,

182
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,639
besides that courtyard,

183
00:21:57,639 --> 00:22:00,990
is there anything else suspicious there?

184
00:22:01,839 --> 00:22:03,359
Yes.

185
00:22:03,359 --> 00:22:07,280
That day, I saw Jing Yi Ming
take a girl covered in wounds into his bedroom.

186
00:22:07,280 --> 00:22:08,953
It reminded me of what happened to Xiao Yun,

187
00:22:08,953 --> 00:22:10,599
so I kept a close watch.

188
00:22:10,599 --> 00:22:12,406
That night, I saw Jing Yi Ming leave,

189
00:22:12,406 --> 00:22:14,627
so I went inside to have a look.

190
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:22,260
Those beasts.

191
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:25,209
Thank you.

192
00:22:27,279 --> 00:22:30,359
I'm just applying medicine for you.

193
00:22:30,359 --> 00:22:32,440
Mrs. Jing,

194
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:34,032
even though I am usually

195
00:22:34,032 --> 00:22:36,599
locked away in that secret chamber,

196
00:22:36,599 --> 00:22:38,359
I still know

197
00:22:38,359 --> 00:22:41,240
that you are not like him.

198
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:44,000
I can often hear you

199
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:46,000
quarreling with him.

200
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:49,000
You always pray for his victims.

201
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,680
Burn paper for them too.

202
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,879
You try to persuade him to stop.

203
00:22:52,879 --> 00:22:55,240
Even if he beats you for it,

204
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:57,886
you have never stopped.

205
00:23:03,879 --> 00:23:05,480
I beg you, Mrs. Jing.

206
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:08,279
Give me a pot of poisoned alcohol.

207
00:23:08,279 --> 00:23:10,680
I want to kill him myself

208
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:12,707
to avenge my elder brother.

209
00:23:13,279 --> 00:23:14,920
Don't.

210
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,880
Give up that idea immediately.

211
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:19,319
If you fail, you will surely die.

212
00:23:19,319 --> 00:23:21,267
Even if I die,

213
00:23:21,839 --> 00:23:24,497
I must try.

214
00:23:27,320 --> 00:23:29,160
To tell you the truth,

215
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:32,279
you are not the first person
he has locked up.

216
00:23:32,279 --> 00:23:34,340
Over the years,

217
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:35,900
I have seen too many girls

218
00:23:35,900 --> 00:23:39,200
who would risk their lives to take his life.

219
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,760
But in the end,

220
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:42,559
they were just rolled in straw mats

221
00:23:42,559 --> 00:23:44,440
and thrown into a mass grave.

222
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:46,320
Once your life is gone,

223
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:49,142
how can you talk about revenge?

224
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:53,396
The time has not yet come.

225
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:56,480
All you can do now

226
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:58,774
is wait.

227
00:24:03,599 --> 00:24:05,760
Chief Jing.

228
00:24:08,879 --> 00:24:11,079
I was afraid you would have scars,

229
00:24:11,079 --> 00:24:13,559
so I told her to apply medicine for you.

230
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:16,140
Yet you ungrateful wretch. Try to kill me?

231
00:24:16,140 --> 00:24:18,300
Let go!

232
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:29,319
"The time has not yet come"? Then tell me,

233
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:31,858
when will the time come?

234
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,519
It has been ten years.

235
00:24:34,519 --> 00:24:38,200
You have committed enough sins in these years.

236
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:39,719
Let Yu Lian go.

237
00:24:39,719 --> 00:24:41,279
No more sins.

238
00:24:41,279 --> 00:24:43,480
Or you will pay for what you've done!

239
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:45,120
Pay?

240
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:48,080
If there were any justice,
I would have paid ten years ago.

241
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:51,120
When I ordered Su Yi Zhou
to set your Bawang Manor against Linyuan Sect.

242
00:24:51,120 --> 00:24:53,239
When your whole house was put to the sword.

243
00:24:53,239 --> 00:24:55,439
That was on me.

244
00:24:55,439 --> 00:24:56,920
But now,

245
00:24:56,920 --> 00:25:00,686
am I not standing here perfectly fine?

246
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:03,800
Rest assured.

247
00:25:03,800 --> 00:25:07,253
I will find someone to treat you well.

248
00:25:16,199 --> 00:25:18,560
At that time, I couldn't rescue Mrs. Jing

249
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,719
and that girl named Yu Lian.

250
00:25:20,719 --> 00:25:23,959
I think since I knew she was locked up
in Jing's secret chamber,

251
00:25:23,959 --> 00:25:26,560
I'll definitely have a chance to rescue her.

252
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:28,199
So Yu Lian

253
00:25:28,199 --> 00:25:31,653
is the witness who saw He Bo's true face.

254
00:25:34,093 --> 00:25:38,400
So, the conflict between Bawang Manor
and Linyuan Sect back then

255
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:41,160
was actually orchestrated by Jing Yi Ming.

256
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:44,999
In that case,
his scheme was set in motion ten years ago.

257
00:25:44,999 --> 00:25:46,279
That means

258
00:25:46,279 --> 00:25:48,439
Mrs. Jing must know a lot of things too.

259
00:25:48,439 --> 00:25:50,759
She can also be a witness.

260
00:25:50,759 --> 00:25:52,199
At this point,

261
00:25:52,199 --> 00:25:54,606
we finally have a lead.

262
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:58,839
Zhao Hui.

263
00:25:58,839 --> 00:26:01,039
There's something I can't hide from you.

264
00:26:01,039 --> 00:26:02,680
In the secret chamber,

265
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:04,759
I saw Zhanlu Sword.

266
00:26:04,759 --> 00:26:08,973
Jing Yi Ming must have fought with your father.

267
00:26:10,319 --> 00:26:13,319
So Jing Yi Ming really did kill my father.

268
00:26:13,319 --> 00:26:15,400
It's not just your father.

269
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:18,400
I think every weapon

270
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:20,120
displayed in that chamber

271
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:22,723
has a life behind it.

272
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,600
Jing Yi Ming also wants to use the banquet

273
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:29,400
to force all sects to serve Lord of Xiangyang.

274
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,360
It's too dangerous for you at Jing's house.

275
00:26:31,360 --> 00:26:34,496
Find a way to get out quickly.

276
00:26:35,279 --> 00:26:36,720
No, Brother Zhan.

277
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,680
I must stay at Jing's house.

278
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:40,600
Firstly, it's for Yue Hua.

279
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:41,640
Secondly,

280
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,680
since you're investigating Jing,

281
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,440
someone needs to stay inside

282
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:48,206
to help you find clues.

283
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:56,600
Zhao Hui,

284
00:26:56,600 --> 00:26:58,440
be very careful back at Jing's house.

285
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,600
If anything goes wrong,

286
00:26:59,600 --> 00:27:01,279
find a way to get out immediately.

287
00:27:01,279 --> 00:27:03,795
Don't worry, Brother Zhan.

288
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:07,519
I'll keep a close eye out

289
00:27:07,519 --> 00:27:09,079
for Yue Hua's whereabouts.

290
00:27:09,079 --> 00:27:10,440
If there's any news,

291
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,860
I'll inform you immediately.

292
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:13,660
Okay.

293
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:18,190
Farewell.

294
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:31,440
No wonder Brother Ding
risked his life to stay at Jing's house.

295
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,939
He even thought of handing the suspect
to the authorities.

296
00:27:33,939 --> 00:27:36,535
That is truly admirable.

297
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:40,680
If my family's blood was on that man's hands,

298
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:43,557
I wouldn't let anyone else strike the blow.

299
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:45,640
I fear

300
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,200
that the path Yue Hua wants to take

301
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:49,952
is exactly the one you mentioned.

302
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,319
Miss Huo,

303
00:27:55,319 --> 00:27:57,120
when we first met, you said you knew

304
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:59,400
the young master of Tang Sect.

305
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,519
How close is your friendship?

306
00:28:01,519 --> 00:28:05,496
We've known each other since childhood.
We're best friends.

307
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,586
Since you are close friends,

308
00:28:07,586 --> 00:28:09,239
then he must be chivalrous,

309
00:28:09,239 --> 00:28:10,600
just like you.

310
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:11,839
Of course.

311
00:28:11,839 --> 00:28:13,360
He is kind by nature,

312
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:17,446
and would never get involved
in the Tang Sect's dirty dealings.

313
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,198
Zhan,

314
00:28:20,198 --> 00:28:22,908
why do you ask about him all of a sudden?

315
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,839
I want to ask him for a favor.

316
00:28:27,839 --> 00:28:29,759
Bai Yu Tang is acting so strangely

317
00:28:29,759 --> 00:28:32,640
because his two sworn brothers
haven't been cured of the poison.

318
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,720
I suspect

319
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:35,920
Zhi Hua is using the antidote as a threat,

320
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:39,154
forcing Bai Yu Tang
to act against his conscience.

321
00:28:39,759 --> 00:28:41,160
But tonight,

322
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,839
Jing Yi Ming said

323
00:28:42,839 --> 00:28:45,857
there is no antidote for Yemotian Poison.

324
00:28:47,180 --> 00:28:49,079
So, you mean...

325
00:28:49,079 --> 00:28:52,239
you want Xiao Tang to make an antidote?

326
00:28:52,239 --> 00:28:54,890
For now, we can only try.

327
00:28:55,600 --> 00:28:56,920
No problem.

328
00:28:56,920 --> 00:28:58,720
The Tang Sect's base is in Xiangyang.

329
00:28:58,720 --> 00:29:00,360
I'll go find him tomorrow.

330
00:29:00,360 --> 00:29:03,160
Xiao Tang has always studied these poisons.

331
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:05,880
I'm sure he can help.

332
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:07,982
Tell him I'm grateful.

333
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:15,080
That Zhi Hua...

334
00:29:15,080 --> 00:29:17,960
How dare he toy with Brother Bai like that.

335
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:21,393
Once this is over, I'll teach him a lesson.

336
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,839
And that Rat Bai too.

337
00:29:26,839 --> 00:29:28,960
That Rat Bai is also despicable.

338
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:30,999
He didn't tell us about such a serious matter.

339
00:29:30,999 --> 00:29:32,920
He doesn't treat us as friends at all.

340
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:35,160
If you hadn't noticed the signs,

341
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:37,479
wouldn't we have delayed
saving those two brothers?

342
00:29:37,479 --> 00:29:40,279
And we fell for Zhi Hua's scheme.
Divided us for nothing.

343
00:29:40,279 --> 00:29:42,079
Before we deal with Zhi Hua,

344
00:29:42,079 --> 00:29:45,043
we should teach that Rat Bai a lesson first.

345
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:48,160
You're right.

346
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,519
But for now,

347
00:29:49,519 --> 00:29:52,079
let's not rush to punish Rat Bai.

348
00:29:52,079 --> 00:29:53,239
The priority now

349
00:29:53,239 --> 00:29:55,319
is to rescue Yu Lian before the banquet.

350
00:29:55,319 --> 00:29:57,880
We need her to testify against He Bo.

351
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,319
Understood.

352
00:29:59,319 --> 00:30:03,205
That way, we can prevent that banquet's trap.

353
00:30:14,039 --> 00:30:18,319
If Brother Bai can't find the magistrate,
he'll surely come back to find us.

354
00:30:18,319 --> 00:30:21,640
He'll definitely be in a foul mood again.

355
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:23,200
His mouth is

356
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:24,799
even sharper than a blade.

357
00:30:24,799 --> 00:30:27,132
His words cut straight to the heart.

358
00:30:27,999 --> 00:30:30,720
Then let's prepare some fish for him.

359
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:34,053
That should shut him up and stop his nagging.

360
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:38,400
It's actually quite strange.

361
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,160
The two of you are opposites.

362
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:42,120
You're a cat who doesn't like fish,

363
00:30:42,120 --> 00:30:43,460
while he's a mouse

364
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:46,540
who can't live a day without it.

365
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,720
Didn't you say

366
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:01,880
that Zhongxiao Pavilion

367
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:04,039
already had extra guards?

368
00:31:04,039 --> 00:31:06,836
How did Zhan Zhao get in?

369
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,520
Zhi Hua.

370
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:09,766
Didn't you say you'd take

371
00:31:09,766 --> 00:31:11,812
full responsibility for arranging the guards?

372
00:31:11,812 --> 00:31:14,039
How do you explain this?

373
00:31:14,039 --> 00:31:17,200
Chief, I am still investigating the matter.

374
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,880
What's there to investigate?

375
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:21,759
That Bai Yu Tang
must be working with them from the inside

376
00:31:21,759 --> 00:31:23,440
to help them sneak in.

377
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,759
You thought you were clever

378
00:31:24,759 --> 00:31:26,479
by turning Bai Yu Tang to our side.

379
00:31:26,479 --> 00:31:28,360
You thought you could lead everyone,

380
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:31,853
but you're the one being played.

381
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,920
Chief.

382
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:37,920
Zhan Zhao knows your plan for the banquet.

383
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:40,440
He will surely try to sabotage it.

384
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,440
I request permission

385
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,263
to eliminate this major threat

386
00:31:43,263 --> 00:31:45,039
before the birthday banquet begins.

387
00:31:45,039 --> 00:31:47,039
You? eliminate him?

388
00:31:47,039 --> 00:31:49,319
I heard even father only fought him to a draw.

389
00:31:49,319 --> 00:31:51,822
You say you want to eliminate him?

390
00:31:56,360 --> 00:32:00,079
Fine. I will leave this matter to you.

391
00:32:00,079 --> 00:32:03,200
- Yes.
- You must eliminate Zhan Zhao...

392
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:05,773
before the birthday banquet.

393
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:09,519
Father. On my way back,

394
00:32:09,519 --> 00:32:11,079
I saw that Ding lad.

395
00:32:11,079 --> 00:32:14,400
He reeked of alcohol,
as if he had just returned from a tavern.

396
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:16,440
He was drunk?

397
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,559
But I wonder,

398
00:32:17,559 --> 00:32:19,920
is he truly drunk,

399
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:22,475
or is he just faking it?

400
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,600
We lost Jiao Chao Gui.

401
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:32,160
Those old fogies won't give in so easily.

402
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:34,239
They need a bit of a warning.

403
00:32:34,239 --> 00:32:35,720
In that case,

404
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:38,120
I'll let them see clearly
what happened to the Ding family.

405
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:39,239
I'll let them know

406
00:32:39,239 --> 00:32:41,960
the consequences of opposing me.

407
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:44,239
Keep Ding Zhao Hui alive for now.

408
00:32:44,239 --> 00:32:46,200
At the birthday banquet,

409
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:48,733
I'll make an example of him.

410
00:32:50,999 --> 00:32:53,858
His death will send a message.

411
00:32:58,953 --> 00:33:01,039
- Zhan.
- You're awake.

412
00:33:01,039 --> 00:33:02,799
Why didn't you sleep a bit longer?

413
00:33:02,799 --> 00:33:06,120
My thoughts keep me from resting.

414
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,519
I want to go to Tang Sect as soon as possible.

415
00:33:07,519 --> 00:33:10,520
Once we have the antidote,
I'm sure Brother Bai will return.

416
00:33:10,520 --> 00:33:12,858
I'll rely on you then.

417
00:33:14,519 --> 00:33:17,079
I saw the candlelight in your room
stayed lit all night.

418
00:33:17,079 --> 00:33:19,079
You're also thinking about the rescue?

419
00:33:19,079 --> 00:33:20,239
Yes.

420
00:33:20,239 --> 00:33:22,079
I have a preliminary plan.

421
00:33:22,079 --> 00:33:23,680
But with only a few of us,

422
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:26,006
it won't be enough.

423
00:34:40,079 --> 00:34:42,709
Why did you want to see me?

424
00:34:50,559 --> 00:34:52,600
I have many affairs in Hanshui Palace.

425
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:54,640
If there's nothing urgent,

426
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:56,869
I'll take my leave.

427
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,999
I want to rescue Yu Lian

428
00:34:59,999 --> 00:35:02,600
and the girls from Zhongxiao Pavilion.

429
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:05,720
I wonder if you could introduce me, Moon Envoy,

430
00:35:05,720 --> 00:35:08,636
to meet Granny Hanshui.

431
00:35:10,239 --> 00:35:12,836
You want Granny to help you?

432
00:35:14,720 --> 00:35:17,160
Granny will not help you.

433
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:19,519
She may pity the girls of Zhongxiao Pavilion,

434
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:21,000
but she would never risk

435
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:23,200
the entire Hanshui Palace. Not in her nature.

436
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:26,000
Furthermore,
Zhongxiao Pavilion is heavily guarded now.

437
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,720
Zhi Hua is waiting for a chance to kill you.

438
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:29,119
Under such circumstances,

439
00:35:29,119 --> 00:35:30,720
how do you plan to save them?

440
00:35:30,720 --> 00:35:34,119
Even if there is only a glimmer of hope,

441
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:36,895
I must give it my best shot.

442
00:35:53,959 --> 00:35:55,640
Don't move, please!

443
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:58,200
Don't move!

444
00:35:58,200 --> 00:35:59,359
Careful! Careful!

445
00:35:59,359 --> 00:36:02,080
One step on a Love Bug sprout,
another on a Blood-Withered Grass!

446
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:04,240
[Tang Tian Hao, Young Master of the Tang Sect]
My treasures wrong you somehow?

447
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:07,733
Come out! Don't step on them! Careful, careful!

448
00:36:10,120 --> 00:36:12,006
I've brought you a very novel poison.

449
00:36:12,006 --> 00:36:14,562
I'm sure you've never seen it.

450
00:36:24,399 --> 00:36:26,359
Despite having examined countless poisons,

451
00:36:26,359 --> 00:36:28,999
I have rarely seen such an exquisite one.

452
00:36:28,999 --> 00:36:30,319
Brilliant.

453
00:36:30,319 --> 00:36:32,439
Can you make an antidote?

454
00:36:33,439 --> 00:36:35,600
Three months.

455
00:36:35,600 --> 00:36:37,959
Three days. If I needed three months,

456
00:36:37,959 --> 00:36:39,200
I, the Young Master of Tang Sect,

457
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:41,359
would be nothing but a fraud.

458
00:36:41,359 --> 00:36:45,255
I knew you would have no problem,
Young Master of Tang Sect.

459
00:36:47,479 --> 00:36:48,640
Ling Long.

460
00:36:48,640 --> 00:36:50,086
I can make its antidote,

461
00:36:50,086 --> 00:36:51,799
but I don't want to.

462
00:36:51,799 --> 00:36:53,439
Unless you give me an explanation,

463
00:36:53,439 --> 00:36:55,855
I will never help you.

464
00:36:56,879 --> 00:36:58,600
What explanation?

465
00:36:58,600 --> 00:37:00,986
I'm asking you.

466
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:19,839
After you fled the wedding,
why did you go to Xiao Zhao instead of me?

467
00:37:19,839 --> 00:37:20,959
You have no idea

468
00:37:20,959 --> 00:37:22,799
how he boasted in that letter.

469
00:37:22,799 --> 00:37:23,839
And another thing.

470
00:37:23,839 --> 00:37:26,260
You and Zhan Zhao only met by chance.

471
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:28,359
Why did you go off to roam the world with him?

472
00:37:28,359 --> 00:37:30,560
You didn't even think to come and see me.

473
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:32,240
Roam the world?

474
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:34,359
Zhan Zhao and I were solving a case.

475
00:37:34,359 --> 00:37:36,560
We were very busy.

476
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:39,479
You went through life and death together.

477
00:37:39,479 --> 00:37:40,700
Doesn't that mean he'll soon

478
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:42,353
be as important to you as I am,
your childhood friend--

479
00:37:42,353 --> 00:37:43,479
Enough.

480
00:37:43,479 --> 00:37:44,919
Saving lives is more important.

481
00:37:44,919 --> 00:37:47,080
Besides, I'm not here for Zhan Zhao today.

482
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:49,560
- I'm here for Bai Yu Tang.
- What?

483
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:51,919
Now there is a Bai Yu Tang?
Why is it so complicated?

484
00:37:51,919 --> 00:37:54,560
What's going on in that head of yours?

485
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:55,760
In your mind,

486
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:58,240
is everything I do for the sake of romance?

487
00:37:58,240 --> 00:38:00,926
Can't it be for justice?

488
00:38:01,999 --> 00:38:03,319
Let's talk business.

489
00:38:03,319 --> 00:38:04,720
The Yemotian Poison matter

490
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:07,319
concerns many lives.

491
00:38:07,319 --> 00:38:10,595
Developing its antidote is no laughing matter.

492
00:38:11,680 --> 00:38:12,720
Fine.

493
00:38:12,720 --> 00:38:13,999
I really want to help you.

494
00:38:13,999 --> 00:38:15,319
I'm just worried that

495
00:38:15,319 --> 00:38:18,560
if my uncle finds out about this,
he'll be very unhappy.

496
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:21,479
Wasn't your uncle's position as Chief
passed down to him by your father?

497
00:38:21,479 --> 00:38:24,319
You, a young master. Afraid of him?

498
00:38:24,319 --> 00:38:25,760
Actually, I...

499
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:29,439
Didn't you always complain to me
about his actions before?

500
00:38:29,439 --> 00:38:30,872
Now that you've grown up,

501
00:38:30,872 --> 00:38:32,839
you should have your own opinions.

502
00:38:32,839 --> 00:38:34,399
Developing the antidote

503
00:38:34,399 --> 00:38:36,799
is the first step in standing up to him.

504
00:38:36,799 --> 00:38:38,600
Me, standing up to him?

505
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:40,120
With just my skills?

506
00:38:40,120 --> 00:38:41,858
No way.

507
00:38:45,736 --> 00:38:47,879
Could it be that you can't make the antidote?

508
00:38:47,879 --> 00:38:49,680
You said three days.

509
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:51,862
Bragging.

510
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:56,240
Three days it is.

511
00:38:56,240 --> 00:38:58,577
I will not go back on my word.

512
00:39:00,240 --> 00:39:03,359
Brother Zhan, I understand your plan.

513
00:39:03,359 --> 00:39:04,999
I just thought of someone

514
00:39:04,999 --> 00:39:06,439
who might share my thoughts

515
00:39:06,439 --> 00:39:08,600
and could help us.

516
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:09,839
But right now,

517
00:39:09,839 --> 00:39:12,319
the Jing family has halted
all birthday banquet preparations.

518
00:39:12,319 --> 00:39:14,279
It seems they're going all out to kill you

519
00:39:14,279 --> 00:39:16,080
to eliminate any future trouble.

520
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:19,399
Brother Zhan, you have no chance to sneak in.

521
00:39:19,399 --> 00:39:21,279
Zhao Hui, don't worry.

522
00:39:21,279 --> 00:39:22,786
Make sure to protect yourself first.

523
00:39:22,786 --> 00:39:24,086
If you sense any danger,

524
00:39:24,086 --> 00:39:25,319
you must leave immediately.

525
00:39:25,319 --> 00:39:28,110
Alright. I'll head back then.

526
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:36,080
Did Zhan Zhao go in?

527
00:41:36,080 --> 00:41:38,827
Yes. Should we strike now?

528
00:41:39,680 --> 00:41:41,919
Wait.

529
00:41:41,919 --> 00:41:44,194
Wait a little longer.

530
00:42:19,999 --> 00:42:21,613
Zhan.

531
00:42:22,240 --> 00:42:24,040
Xiao Tang has agreed to work on the antidote.

532
00:42:24,040 --> 00:42:26,779
It's crawling with Zhi Hua's men outside.
We must leave now.

533
00:42:38,799 --> 00:42:41,130
Brother Bai.

534
00:42:51,040 --> 00:42:53,040
Give me that corrupt official.

535
00:42:53,040 --> 00:42:55,220
We know all

536
00:42:55,220 --> 00:42:57,560
about Zhi Hua threatening you.

537
00:42:57,560 --> 00:43:00,279
There is no antidote for Yemotian Poison.

538
00:43:00,279 --> 00:43:03,418
Don't let Zhi Hua manipulate you.

539
00:43:03,418 --> 00:43:05,809
Give him to me.
